which collected 41 million in the 15month period and spent 21 
million 
but in that same category the realtors pac gave the most to 
candidates reporting 789000 in contributions compared with the 
ama pacs 542037 
the realtors group was second to the ama in fund raising in this 
category collecting 32 million in the 15month period 
