declaration encompassing all the political economic technological 
and cultural aspects of our relationship 
on saturday he said such a declaration must be followed by a 
europeanamerican treaty aimed at shaping the future he did not 
elaborate as to what that might specifically entail but said the 
right decision to reduce political and military tension must not be 
replaced by a wrong decision to engage in wars of trade and 
technology 
