measured it at 71 on the richter scale 
a number of houses and buildings have been reported damaged in 
juba 750 miles south of khartoum whose population has been 
swelled by refugees no injuries have been reported in juba 
however 
the richter scale is a measure of ground motion as recorded on 
seismographs every increase of one number means a tenfold increase 
in magnitude thus a reading of 71 reflects an earthquake 10 times 
stronger than one of 61 
