of the revolution on dec 22 just hours before his parents fled 
bucharest when the army decided to back the revolution 
nicolae and elena ceausescu were arrested convicted of genocide 
at a summary military trial and executed on dec 25 
nicu ceausescu testified that on the morning of dec 22 police 
and leaders of the local securitate told him they were being shot 
